FeldWert
NameJAR Install Plugin
BeschreibungMaven plugin to download jar files and install them as artifact into the local maven repository. Additional the artifacts will be added to the dependency list of maven project.
Webseitehttps://github.com/FunThomas424242/jar-install-plugin/
